text:
Today I was thinking about sorrow;
Probably the only thing I am expert at.
Spend so much time with it;
Shouldn't have any problem with that.

But you know, sometimes it hurt ;
Sometimes it pain.
To get a relase from it ;
I don't know what I have to gain.


Whatever, I still love tragedy;
In real life that's how most stories end;
Just like think about betrayal,
It always comes from your closest friends.

I have thousands dreams ;
But I priorities a few.
This one is special ;
cause it's about you.

There will be a day ;
when we will be together.
Walking beside , holding hands ;
And nothing can make us bother. 

No care about world , No tension ;
There will be just me and you.
Suddenly I will stop , Bend on my knees
And again I will tell you " I Love You" .
